<br>
For example, I parsed a primal 2-hander (45/44) Versus a Willsaper and Primal 1-hander (both 13/20).  I got around ~75 with the 2h (1300 atk) and ~65 dual wielding, from the front.<br>
<br>
Although I like to dual wield, they lost *alot* of viability with the changes mid-velious and the huge damage you get from PoP-ripostes.<br>
<br>
Edit:  This was done fighting various trash in PoV desert, mostly golems. <p>Veteran <a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=34639>Damacis Bigadanu</a>
